snippet.title: Balance of Power Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for the upcoming visual novel, Balance of Power.
Trailer edited by Lilly Murphy. Music made by Ben Murphy. 

Check out our Demo on Itch.io here: https://camicarriedo.itch.io/balance-of-power
And our Kickstarter here: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/balance-of-power/balance-of-power-visual-novel
